\id LEV Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93 
\h LIPITIKASE 
\toc1 LIPITIKASE 
\toc2 Lipitikase 
\toc3 Li 
\mt1 LIPITIKASE  
\imt1 Lipae Akali Dupwana Purisi Yulu  
\ip Buku Lipitikase lenge dakena purisi akali dupwana yulu pyasi palamo. Wambu dupwame mena kiso Anatu lakandarami lao wato leyaminyi dokopa rara mende Lipae lenge dokona purisi dupwa rapu pyuo kareyami. Anatumi wambu dupwa pimili yaka lao suu piyamo dupwa purisi akali dupwame wambu dupwa Anatu yulu dake pinya letamo doko mana lao kareyami. Buku dakena renge mende palamo doko Anatunya poo pyasi renge doko. Isaraele wambu dupwa Anatu lakando wambu dapwa Anatu baapa role pyao yalya kando karalu karo kararami lao renge dupwa opetae pyasi palamo.  
\ip Buku dake mendaki sipyamopape arome pii kingi paki liti pipala pyasi palamo.  
\io1 \bk 1. Rombo 1-7 \bk*Mawa pii Anatu lakando mena kisingi dokona lao pyasi palamo.  
\io1 \bk 2. Rombo 8-10 \bk*Eronepa ikinyingimoo dupwa pipya nakama purisi ingyuo kanda soo kareyaminyi dokopa yuu gii dokona lao pyasi palamo.  
\io1 \bk 3. Rombo 11-15 \bk*Mawa pii wambo piyaminyi dupwa moŋo nyiyaminyi dokopa Anatumi namba karo peteyamosa randa jero dopa letamo lao suu piyami. Rombo dusipa dakena karo petenge mawa pii wambarae dupwa pyasi palamo.  
\io1 \bk 4. Rombo 16 \bk*Anatumi Wambunya Koo Nyuo Nembakamiyamo Yuu Gii dokona lao pyasi palamo.  
\io1 \bk 5. Rombo 17-27 \bk*Wambu dupwa mee yulu pyuo Anatu lakando apa pyuo poo pyasi ingyuo karalu karo kareyami lao mawa pii dupwa pyasi palamo.  
\ip Buku dakena pii malu mee palipyamopape pii kuki mende wambu ama malu mee kame see nange. Pii kuki dake rombo 19 liti 18 dokona pyasi palamo.  
\ip Yesu pii dokona lao dopa leyapya. Mawa pii mendaki ikimi mawa pii dake isa palyilyamo, leya. Nakama range kando mona retenge doko suu pyao wambu maki palenge dupwa mona reto karalapape, leya.  
\is1 1:1—15:33  
\ip Rombo 1-7 dupwana Isaraele wambu dupwame bangepe mena pyao kisingipi Anatu maiyami lao palamo. Rombo 8-10 dupwana nakamame Eronemoo banya ikinyingi dupwape purisi yulu pirami lao nakamana kyawa wele kiso rombo palyuo kareyami lao palamo. Rombo 11-14 lowa lengenyili pyuo wambu dupwa poo pyasi ingyuo kareyami lao palamo. Nakamame mena rara lapo iki neyami. Lapo naa nayami. Enda dupwa nyaŋa kando nyepala apa pyuo dee au pyuo peteyami lao lowa pii lapo palamo. Dee rapa akali dupwana lao pii palamoko.  
\c 16  
\s1 Anatumi Wambunya Koo Nyuo Nembakamiyamo Yuu Gii Andake Doko  
\p
\v 1 Eronena ikinyingi dolapome Kamongona lenge kambu dokona isare kopetame kiso kareyambinyisa nakamba kumuyambinyipa enakana Kamongome Mosese pii lamaiya.  
\v 2 Dopa lamaiyuo, Embame yangone Erone lamaiyuo, Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi dokona namba kopa rakapana epo Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote roma dokona ketae epengeŋe dokona yuu gii angi rolae dokopa iki komau andake yukwaro karamo dokona matarena baa epapa pinya lamairi. Daaŋa lapala larono dokona palyuo pii napala kamba lara ramo doko baa pyao kumakaro.  
\v 3 Wambo baame mena bulamakao kali dusa kanya kanyande wambunya koo dupwana kame sakaminya lao pyao kisakamyuo dee sipisipi kali doko isarena kiso mukunyi nembo maiyuo karapala dokopa Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi dokona sukusa para, leya.   
\p
\v 4 Dokopa enakana Kamongome dopa pinya lamaiya. Erone baa andakare Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi dokona panya karo dokopa ipwame wate pipala purisinya komau dupwa nyuo wapwara. Komau rasisi mende wapupala dee komau keyange londe mende pee pipala dokona ketae marapu mendeme rambu lao wapu pipala komau mendeme kyawa dokona andu pinyi palyara.   
\p
\v 5 Isaraele wambu peparaeme Erone mena meme kali lama wambunya koo dupwana lao pyao kiso mainyale lao maiyuo dee sipisipi kali mende isarena kiso mukinyi nembena lao maiyuo pirami.  
\v 6 Erone baame mena bulamakao mende banya rangena koo dupwanape banya ree palunya koo dupwanape lao pyao yangara.  
\v 7 Dokopa baame Kamongona komau anda kambu konandowame dokona mena meme kali lama nyepala minyuo para.  
\v 8 Baame kana lama nyepala mende Kamongonaŋa lao mende Asasele lengendenaŋa lao reto pipala kana dolapo kanda nao karo mende ipyuo nyera.  
\v 9 Ipyuo nyeramo dokopa mena meme Kamongonaŋa lao rombo palyaramo doko Eroneme wambunya koo dupwana lao pyao kisakamira.  
\v 10 Mena meme Asasele lengendenaŋa lao rombo palyaramo doko lenge rape rape Kamongo maipala yuu muiyane dokona Asasele keta mainyi nembara. Dopa piramo dokome wambunya koo dupwa nyuo nembakamira.   
\p
\v 11 Erone baame banya ree palu dee baa rangepena koo dupwana lao bulamakao kalinde pyao kisakamyuo  
\v 12 dokopa isare pee nembenge kapa mendena isa lengya nyuo simbuo reto dee kingi kape laparaena kete pyao rendamu bange kyaa pingi mende nyuo pipala Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi dokona peparae minyuo para.  
\v 13 Papala dokopa Kamongona lenge kambu dokona bange rendamu pingi doko isarena retara. Retaramo dokopa rendamu pingi bange dokona sukwa dokome Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote roma doko yambe pyara. Yambe pyaramo dokona Erone baame doko kandapala kuma nara.  
\v 14 Baame mena bulamakao kali dokona ranjama lapo nyepala kingi pambu dokome minyuo pyarenda lanyi bokote roma lenge kambusa pisara. Pisapala dee Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote seramo dokona lenge kambusa yuu yanda ipingi nyepo ranjama dokome pyarendanyi pisara.   
\p
\v 15 Pisapala baame mena memende wambunya koo dupwana lao pyapala dokona ranjama nyepala Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi dokona minyuo epo bulamakaona ranjama dokome wambo piyamuli pyuo baame bokote roma dokonape Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote dokona lenge kambusa dokonape pyarendanyi pisara.  
\v 16 Yulu dopa piramo dokopa Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi doko pyuo elya pinyi retara. Isaraele wambu nakama keyange ingya nao Anatupa kamba koo lao kareyaminyisa banya Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi doko kokwa siyamisa piyamo dokona Eroneme baa dopako pira. Yuu paleyaminyi doko poo pyasi ingya napyamo sukusa dokona Anatunya komau anda karapyamosa Erone baame dopako pira.  
\v 17 Erone baame banya koope dee banya ree palunya koope Isaraele wambu peparaena koope dupwa nyuo kame sakaminya lao yulu piramo mange dokopa komau anda andakare dokona wambu mendepe pisa nara.  
\v 18 Dokopa baame Anatunya lao kana pyare lasi dokona kiso mukinyi nembo maingi doko elyape inginyi pyambuo para. Dopa pyuo dokopa mena bulamakao kalinya ranjamape dee memena ranjama lapo nyepala kana pyare pinjingi kisima siyamo dusipana raeyo reto pira.  
\v 19 Banya kingi pambu dokome ranjama doko nyepala kana pyare lasi dokona yuu yanda ipingi nyepo pyarenda lanyi pisara. Dopa piramo dokome Isaraele wambunya koo dupwame kana pyare lasi kokwa siyaminyi doko keyange inginyi pyambuo poo pyarasa pira.   
\s1 Meme Mendeme Koo Dupwa Nyuo Peya  
\p
\v 20 Eroneme Panda Kamame Poo Pyasipi Kamongona komau anda panda wakalepe kana pyare lasipi dusipana mondo lao pyuo rolo otapala dokopa mena meme mende lenge rao Asaselena rombo palyisi doko kararamopa Kamongo keta minyuo epo maira.  
\v 21 Maipala banya kingi dolapo memena ayemba dokona ketae retaro karo Isaraele wambunya yulu koope kamba lao Anatu mata maiyuo yulu pingipi polo lamaiyuo memena ayemba keta pisara. Pisapala akali mendeme meme doko nyuo lanyuo neta para lao rombo palyiyami dokome yuu muiyane dokona meme mapanyi nembara.  
\v 22 Mena meme dokome Isaraele wambunya koo dupwa nyepala paleta wambu pali nange panda keroŋo mendena para.   
\p
\v 23 Yulu doko pyuo otapala dokopa Erone baame Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi dorena kolandalana karo purisi komau wapuyamo dupwa Kamongona komau anda dokona papala roko neta nyuo retara.  
\v 24 Retapala baame yuu poo pyasi dokona wate pipala rangena komau doko nyuo wapupala pao baa rangenape dee wambu dupwanape koo dupwana lao mena isarena kiso mukinyi nembara.  
\v 25 Baame kana pyare lasi dokona wambunya koo dupwana lao mena pyao kiso maiyamo dokona kapa rukisi dupwa kisakamira.  
\v 26 Akali mena meme Asaselena lao yuu muiyane dokona mapanyi nembala peyamo doko pao yuu paleyami dokona epana dokopa komau yanengepe wambo wate pipala sukusa kolando epara.  
\v 27 Purisi dokome mena bulamakao kali dee memepe dolapona ranjama nyepala lanyuo Panda Kamame Poo Pyasi dokona koo dupwana nyuo kame soo nembakana lao minyuo kolandeya. Bulamakaope memepe dolapona yanenge ingi minjupi dupwa peparae yuu kame netarena minyuo papala kisinyi nembara.  
\v 28 Akali kisinyi nembaramo doko yuu paliraminyi dokona kapu kyuo sukusa epana dokopa yanenge komaupi wate pipala epara, leya.   
\s1 Anatumi Wambunya Koo Nyuo Nembakamiyamo Yuu Gii Andake Dokona Ee Kana Yaka Lao Yulu Pingi  
\p
\v 29 Nakamame yuu gii doko kame see napala minyuo karalu kararami. Kana yanda ipingi dokona yuu gii akalisa dokopa Isaraele wambu rangepe dee karala papingi dupwa nakama role pyao palaminyi dupwape nenge wasaka pyuo yulu minyanda nao mee pisirami.  
\v 30 Yuu gii dokopa purisi dokome yulu Kamongome pinya leyamuli pyuo piramopa Kamongome nakamana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakaramopa elyape ingyuo kararami.  
\v 31 Yuu gii doko ama poo pyasi ingyuo sera. Dokopa nakamame nenge wasaka pyuo yulu pii nao mee imambu soo pisirami ingilyamo. Yuu peparae mawa pii dapwa minyuo kararami.  
\v 32 Akali mendeme purisi mupwana yulu pyuo karalana rakangena panda nyeramo doko nakamame rolae pyuo rombo palyuo baa Anatunya yulu iki lili pyuo pinya lao larami. Laraminyi dokopa baame wambunya koo dupwa nyuo kame sakamira lao Anatumi leyamuli pyuo pira. Dopa pyuo pinya piso dokopa purisimi komau wapungi doko nyuo pee pipala  
\v 33 Panda Kamame Poo Pyasipi Kamongona komau anda panda wakalepe kana pyare lasipi purisi akalipi Isaraele wambu peparaepe Anatunya lenge kambu dokona poo pyasi ingyuo sera lao koo dupwa nyuo nembakamira.  
\v 34 Yulu dopale dokopa yuu peparae kaeya nao pipa pyuo kararami. Purisi mupwa baame ee kana yaka lao Isaraele wambu dupwana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakamyuo Anatunya lenge kambu dokona rolae ingyuo petena lao pipa pira, leya.  
\p Dokona Kamongome leyamuli pyuo Moseseme piya.   
\s3 17:1—18:30 Rombo 17 Anatunya anda mupwa dokona iki mena pyao kiso maiyami. Dee wambu dupwame ranjamape minju ranjama paletape naa nayami, letamo. Rombo 18 dokona kata anjukunya enda akalipa rolae paleyambi lao letamo.  
\c 19  
\s1 Poo Pyasi Ingyuo Rolae Pyuo Kararami Lao Lowa Pii Dasipa Minyarami  
\p
\v 1 Kamongome Mosese Isaraele wambu dupwa lamainya lao lamaiyuo,  
\v 2 Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatu poo pyasi karo dokona lao nakama poo pyasi karalapape, leya.  
\v 3 Nakama mendaki mendaki lao suu pingi dokona embena endangi rakangepa dolapo angingyuo karambinyi lao rape rape lao suu pyaro karalapape. Karapala nambame leyonoli pyuo koro petenge gii doko minyaro karalapape. Namba Kamongo doko nakamana Anatuŋu karo.  
\v 4 Namba kame soo yaki nyuo kingimi wasisi dupwa anatuŋu lao mona nyii nalapape. Mee kapa pyakepasi dupwame kiso wambu ingyuo wasapala anatuŋu lao lakanda nalapape. Namba Kamongo doko nakamana Anatu doko namba karo kande.   
\p
\v 5 Nakama mona mendare palyuo yalya kando karo mena pyao kisaraminyi dokopa mawa pii lapo langyuo kandapi dupwa minyuo suu pyao kisarami ramo dokopa mona yuu lao nyero.  
\v 6 Minju angi dupwa pyao kisaraminyi yuu gii dokopape panda dokona yangamape dolapona iki napala yuu gii repo pyuo siya kande dupwa naa nao mee kisinyi nembarami.  
\v 7 Mena yuu repona seramo doko poo pyasi ingya naramosa mendeme napala banya kiso jipyamo doko nyakami nao kaeyaro.  
\v 8 Daaŋa lapala enda akalipi mendeme yuu repo pyuo seramo doko nao lara ramo dokopa bange nambapa lao kiso jisi doko pao mee inginyi pyambuo pirasa pira. Dokona lao baa mee nambana wambuko ingyuo kara nana lao raka lanyi nembaro.   
\p
\v 9 Nakamana ee dokona witi jingi wambu piyamopa pyakepo manjo kande dokopa kame nemba nembasa petamo dupwa petena kaeyalapape. Dee lapo suku dupwana kalyinyi palyiyami kande dupwa dee pao pyakepo manjo nyii nalapape.  
\v 10 Nakamana isa girapo ee dokona jingi lyiyami kande dokopa kana pope dee lapo isapasipi dupwa dee nyela paa nalapape. Pendewa wambu dee wambu wakale lapo nakamana yuunya epo petenge dupwana ingyuo sakaminya kaeyalapape. Namba Kamongo doko nakamana Anatu ingyuo karapunu pilyamo.   
\p
\v 11 Nakama mendena waa naa nao mendena bange doko pii panga soo nyakami nao dee kyambo pii laa nao pipwape.  
\v 12 Wambu mendali kando kinyi lapunu pilyamo lao sinya lapala nambana kingi lapala lamaiyami kande doko dee alowa pii nalapape. Lapala kaeyarami ramo doko seramo dokome nambana kingi doko uki minyuo lara ingyasara. Namba Kamongo doko nakamana Anatuŋu karo.   
\p
\v 13 Nakamame mendalinya bange dupwa waa nyakamyuo pyao koo keta palya nalapape. Akali mendeme embena yulu pyakanya lao nyii kande dokopa yuu gii rolae dokopa banya yole maiyakamipi. Rakya jimwa lao reto yuu mendeko yanga napipi.  
\v 14 Wambu lenge koo dupwa lukumao simili lao bange lapo pao wambo reto kalepoe dupwa kando pii langa lao pii nalapape. Namba Kamongo doko nakamana Anatuŋu karo dokome nakama namba mupwa lao suu pyao pako karalapape.   
\p
\v 15 Nakamame kote mende siyami kande dokopa kinyi lao rolae pyuo lakamipape. Nakamame wambu koo dupwa nyisaramisa kote pii doko mee wini lasarami doko kaeyalapape. Dopako pyuo wambu lapo kingi lengepe dee namba petengepe mupwa ingyuowale kandale lao pako mona manjipala mee nyisaramisa kote doko mee wini lasarami doko ama daa.  
\v 16 Wambu mendena lao wakale dupwa kyambo lamaiya nalapape. Wambu mende moŋo andake nyeramopa kote lakamiraminyipa embena piimi nyisare kata siya kande dokona nyisape. Namba nakamana Kamongo karapunu pilyamo.   
\p
\v 17 Embena andare mendeme emba keta kopetame pyuo pisiya kande doko baapa lao imbu singi doko suu pyanyi pyano kara napipi. Dopa pyuo koo doko emba keta manjo kara narowale lao suu pyao baapa isa piso lao rolapala dokopa banya lao koo mende pii naresa pira.  
\v 18 Embame koo dokona isingi yano nyelana suu pyaa nao dee koo embapa piramo wambu dokopa imbu paleta kara nao pipi. Emba rangena yongo mona nyuo karene doko suu pyao parali maki palenge wambu dupwa mona reto karape. Namba Kamongo doko karo.   
\p
\v 19 Nambana mawa pii letamuli pyuo minyalapape. Nakamana mena bulamakao dupwa mena rara wakale dupwa pipya pyaso kepo pyuo yakane manja kaena dee waingi rara lama minyuo pyaso ee mendakinya wara pii nalapape. Komau eleko rara lamame pyaso wapu nalapape.   
\p
\v 20 Akali mendeme banya kendemande wanake doko akali mendena kalya pyuo mairamo doko yapa nara ramo doko akali kalya pyakamira dokopa yuu lapo role pyao palirambi ramo pyao kuma nao mee kote serami. Renge doko wanake baa akali banya mee kendemande pyuo pisirako.  
\v 21 Dokona lao nyerambinyi akali baame sipisipi kali mende namba Kamongona komau anda kambu kolandowame dokona banya koo pipu dokona lao pyao kisala epenale.  
\v 22 Koo Anatu baapa ingyuo piyamo doko nyuo nembakana lao purisi akalimi mena sipisipi pyao kisaramo dokopa Anatumi nyuo kame sakamira.   
\p
\v 23 Nakama yuu Kenane epo kando nyepala dokopa jingi lyingi isa rara dupwa wara piyami kande dokopa koo ingyasaraŋa ee kana remana naa nao wasaka pyuo kararami.  
\v 24 Ee kana kisima doko epeya kande dokopa ee isa jingi dupwa peparae lyepala namba keta joo nambana kingi ketae pyambuli lao piramisa pira.  
\v 25 Dopa piraminyipape ee kana kingi paki dokopa kanda soo isa jingi lyuo narami. Nakama dopale pirami ramo dokopa isa jingi lyuo kakana pira. Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatuŋu karo.   
\p
\v 26 Minju lapo ranjama paleta siya kande doko naa nalapape. Pipu mauli ropaka kemalipi kingi lenge dokona mendepe nakamame minyalyuo pyuo laa narami.  
\v 27 Nakamana kyawa wangupi angasi pinjingi dupwape pyakepowape pisarami doko daaŋa leto.  
\v 28 Nakama yongo kamu kepaope dee enda akalipi mende kumuyami kande dokopa yanenge kunjowape pii narami. Namba doko Kamongo karapunu pilyamo.   
\p
\v 29 Nakamame nakamana wanene dupwa mee bange anatuŋu lenge tembole anda dupwana kepo yulu pingi dokona pyuo petena lao maiya nalapape. Daaŋa lao maiyuo larami ramo dokopa namba yaki nyepala mee bange anatuŋu lao suu pingi doko mana nyeraminyipa nakamana yuu andape dupwa pamuku yulu dokome simbwara ingilyamo.  
\v 30 Koro petenge yuu gii doko yaki nyii napala misi lao namba lakandenge panda doko kyawa nyuo minyuo karalapape. Namba Kamongoŋo karo.   
\p
\v 31 Nakamame wambu lapome wambu kumasinya imambu pipya ropaka piso singi dupwa keta papala ropaka piso sisaramiŋi doko daa leto. Dopale dupwana pao kale yuku soo pisirami ramo doko nambapa kopeta kapeta kwaeyo sera ingilyamo. Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatuŋu karo.   
\p
\v 32 Nakamame endemo alemope dupwa angingyuo karaminyiŋi lao suu pyao rape rape lao karalapape. Namba Kamongo doko mupwaŋa lao suu pyapala pako karalapape.   
\p
\v 33 Nakamame yuu wakale wambu karala papingi nakamana yuu palaminyi dupwa kando kopetame pyuo randa mai nalapape.  
\v 34 Nakamana rara pipya yulu pyuo nenge rambo lao pilyaminyi doko suu pyaowako doloma pipya pipwape. Nakama range doko mona reto karaminyi suu pingi mendaki dokonako palyuo doloma mona retalapape. Nakama yuu wakale Isipi wambunya yuu dokona karala papingi ingyuo kareyami kande doko apiyakalende ingyuo kareyamape lao dokona suu pyalapape. Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome leto.   
\p
\v 35 Mendeme nakamana bange mende ropo pyao nyelena epeya kande dokopa sikyali pyuo kandapala kuki andake lao nyuo makande pirami dokopa kyambo mendena palyapala uli pili laa nalapape.  
\v 36 Kandokondali pyuo angi dokona sikyali pyuo nyuo makande pyuo kapa kapa ingyuowape lao kenda bange peparae rolae dokona sikyali pipwape. Renge dokona namba nakamana Kamongo Anatuŋu karo. Nakama Isipi dokona kareyaminyipa nambame nyuo lanyuo dae epeyo kande dokome karo lapunu pilyamo.  
\v 37 Namba Kamongo dokome mawa piipi mana pii dupwape jiyu kande dupwa poraiyuo minyuo karalapape.   
\s3 20:1—22:33 Wambupi purisi dupwape karo pisasaramiŋi lao lowa lapo konda pyuo reteya.  
\c 23  
\s1 Yuu Gii Mupwa Nenge Nao Misi Andake Lao Kareyami Dupwa  
\p
\v 1 Kamongome Mosese lamaiyuo,  
\v 2 Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu gii mupwa Anatunya kingi ketae minyalyuo lao elyambu pyuo nenge nao misi andake lao kararaminyi dokopa apa pyuo kararami lao lamaiya.  
\v 3 Yuu pakinyamange dusipa nakamana ingyuo silyamoŋo dusipana yulu pirami. Yanda ipingi dokopa imambu soo pisirama lao suu pyalapape. Yuu gii dokona yulu pii napala elyambu pyuo misi lao pisirami. Yuu anja lapona karare dokona pii mende daa. Koro petenge yuu gii doko namba Kamongona ingyuo silyamo.  
\v 4 Dakepa nambana yuu gii andake dusipana wambu peparae nyuo malu palyuo misi lena lao lao retelyo. Yuu gii angi rolae doko pyaka seramo dokopa embame wambu dupwa dopa pinya dopa pinya lao lamairi.   
\s1 Borete Isi Pyambwa Nangepe Pasopa Nenge Nengepe Yuu Gii Doko  
\p
\v 5 Kamongo kingi ketae pyambuo nenge Pasopa Nenge doko kana mupwa yuu gii akalisa ipisu kisima dokona neta anda penge dokopa pyaka sepa pingi.  
\v 6 Kana dokona yuu gii akalisa ipisu kingi paki dokopa borete isi pyambwa nao nenge yuu gii doko pyaka sepa pingi. Pyaka sepa piramo dokopa nakama borete isi pyambwange doko naa narami.  
\v 7 Yuu gii mupwa dokopa nakama yuu peparae yulu pinginyili pyuo pii napala nambana kingi iki suu pyao lakando pisirami.  
\v 8 Yuu yanda ipingi nyepo Anatu baa nenge kiso mairami. Yuu gii yanda ipingi dokona nakamana nenge nenge yulu dupwana mende minyanda napala misi lao mee pisirami.  
\v 9-10 Nakama Kamongome yuu jipyamo dokona epapala dokopa witi eepe wara pyuo manjo nyiyami kande dokopa wambo kyawa nyuo puu pyarami doko purisi akali dupwa mairami.  
\v 11 Koro petenge yuu gii dokopa yangamana Kamongome nakama kando rolae petaminyi lao soo nyinyaleŋe purisi dokome witi yama doko Kamongo maiyakara.  
\v 12 Yuu gii witi jeraminyi dokopako nakamame mena sipisipi kali yakane ee kana mendaki pasi yanenge kwaeyo rete pyuowape pii nange mende namba joo isarena kiso sunjura pinyi nembarami.  
\v 13 Dokopa role pyapeta nenge reto jerami dokona ingyuo palawa kilokerame lama nyuo isa olipi ipwange pipya pyasapala kiso jerami. Dokona kyaa dokome Kamongo baa soo epe sera. Dokonako ingyuo waene ipwange sanapenge kuki mendakinya (lita mendaki) minyuo konda pyuo jerami.  
\v 14 Nakamame Anatu bange ene maipa napala dokopa witi wambo wambu pingi dupwana kyakape kisasipi witimi wasisi boretepe dupwana mendepe naa narami. Naa naraminyi doko nakamana para pyasi wambu dupwame ee kana peparae dopako pyulu pyuo kararami.   
\s1 Eena Nenge Manjo Nyingi Yuu Gii Dokopa Anatu Maingi Doko  
\p
\v 15 Koro petenge yuu gii dokopa yangamana witi jingi yama mende namba jepala dokopa koro yanda ipingi ingilyape lao yaka lao kararami.  
\v 16 Koro yanda ipingi paparamopa dee yangama (yuu gii 50) dokopa namba Kamongo doko witi enenge lapo jerami.  
\v 17 Ree palu mendaki mendaki laome borete lama lama lao minyuo epo bange angi jilyamanoŋo lao soo jerami. Palawa kilokerame lama nyepala isi kuki pyambuo borete mendaki mendaki lao waso kisapala nakamame witi wambo wambu piyamo jiyaminyili pyuo namba Kamongo dokona lao jerami.  
\v 18 Bange lapo opetae konda pyuo kiso jepenge. Nakamame sipisipi yakane yanda ipingi nyepo ee kana mendaki pasipi bulamakao kali mendaki meme lamape pyao jerami. Mena mumba palyuo yanyi nyuo pisi dupwa jii narami. Bange dusipa Kamongo keta minyuo epo isareme kiso sunjura pinyi nembo jerami. Joo karo dokopa waene witipi opetae dokona konda pyuo jerami. Dokona kyaa dokome namba Kamongo dokome epe soo kararo.  
\v 19 Mena meme kali mendeme koo dupwana lao pyao kiso dee sipisipi yakane kali ee kana mendaki pasi lama nyuo pipala mona mendaki palyuo yalya kando karalana lao jerami.  
\v 20 Purisi dokome boretepe mena sipisipi yakane lamape namba Kamongo doko purisi dupwana lao jilyuŋu lao jera. Jeramo bange dusipa poo pyasi ingyuo para.  
\v 21 Yuu gii dokopa nakamana nenge nenge yulu dupwana mende minyanda napala misi lao mee pisirami. Pisiraminyi dokopa nakamana para pyasi wambu dupwame yuu muu dupwana karo yaka lao dopako pyulu pyuo pyuo kararami.   
\p
\v 22 Nakamana ee dokona witi jingi wambu piyamopa pyakepo manjo kande dokopa kame nemba nembasa petamo dupwa petena kaeyalapape. Dee lapo suku dupwana kalyinyi palyiyami kande dupwa dee pao pyakepo manjo nyii nalapape. Pendewa wambu dee wambu wakale lapo nakamana yuunya epo petenge dupwana ingyuo sakaminya kaeyalapape. Kamongo doko nakamana Anatuŋu.   
\s1 Ee Kana Enenge Ketae Pyambuo Misi Lao Anatu Nenge Kiso Maingi  
\p
\v 23 Kamongome Mosese kando lao,  
\v 24 Kana yanda ipingi dokona yuu gii mupwa dokopa yuu gii angingyuo imambu soo mee pisirami. Dopa pyuo pisiraminyipa bikuli pii laramo dokopa misi lala epo nyuo malu palyarami.  
\v 25 Dokopa nakamana nenge nenge yulu dupwana mendepe pii napala namba Kamongo doko nenge kiso jerami, leya.   
\s1 Anatumi Koo Dupwa Nyuo Nembakamiya Yuu Gii Andake Doko  
\p
\v 26-27 Kamongome Mosese dopa lamaiya. Kana yanda ipingi nyepo dokona yuu gii akalisa dokopa bange lapo wambunya koo dupwana nyuo kame sakaminya lao jerami. Yuu gii dokopa nenge wasaka pyuo misi iki kingi wapambupi lakao pisipala namba Kamongo nenge kiso jerami.  
\v 28 Namba nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokome nakamana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakara lao nakama yulu pii nao mee kararami.  
\v 29 Daaŋa lapala nakama wambu dupwana mendeme yuu gii dokopa nenge nara ramo doko baa nambana wambu ingyuo kara nara.  
\v 30 Mendeme yuu gii dokona yulu pyuo lara ramo doko namba Kamongo rangeme baa pyao kumasero.  
\v 31 Mawa pii dake nakamana para pyao parami dupwane ingyara. Yuu anjale palyuo kararami dokona pii mende daa.  
\v 32 Imambu singi yuu gii angingyuo suu pyao karo yuu gii mange mendaki neta yapao sii piramo dokona piso pao yuu gii akalisana dee neta yalu piramo dokopa nenge kuki injisi mendepe naa narami, leya.   
\s1 Anda Kauwa Pipala Palyuo Nenge Nenge Yuu Gii Doko  
\p
\v 33 Kamongome Mosese kando pii dapa lao Isaraele wambu dupwa lamainya leya.  
\v 34 Kana yanda ipingi dokona yuu gii akalisa ipisu kingi paki dokopa anda kauwana nenge nenge yuu gii doko pyaka sera. Pyaka sepala yuu yanda ipingi dusipana mee sooko para.  
\v 35 Koro dakena yuu gii mupwa dokopa nakama rangena yulu yaki nyepala nyuo malu palyuo namba lakando misi lao pisirami.  
\v 36 Koro dakena yuu gii yaka lao nakamame namba nenge kiso jerami. Jepala yuu gii mange lama karo dokona kamba epo nyuo malu palyuo lakando piso nenge kiso jerami. Yuu gii doko mee misi iki lao piso yulu pii narami.   
\p
\v 37 Yuu gii andake dusipana nakama malu palyuo piso namba lakando nenge kiso joo bange kiso sunjura pinyi nembo witipi waenepe joo mena pyao kiso joo nambame nakama yuu peparae dopa pipwape dapa pipwape lao langiyunuli pyuo piraminyi dokopa nambana kingi ketae pyambuo kararaminyisa pira.  
\v 38 Nakamame koro petenge yuu gii dokopa imambu soo nambana lao suu pyao piso bange maipa pyuope bange joo pii lalu lao lasi dupwana manda manjo paramo dupwa joope dee range lapo maso jimwali lao suu pyao kararaminyipape nakama yuu gii andake dasipa opetae poraiyuo minyuo misi lao bange joo kararami.   
\p
\v 39 Nakamana ee dokona nenge manjo nyuo otapala dokopa kana yanda ipingi dokona yuu gii akalisa ipisu kingi paki dokopa nyuo malu palyuo yuu gii yanda ipingi nyepo nambame langiyunuli pyuo pyuo pisirami. Yuu gii dusipana yuu gii mupwa doko angingyuo imambu soo pisirami.  
\v 40 Nakamame yuu gii mupwa dokona nakamana isa jingi lyingi dupwana lyuo nyuo dee yala isa wangyape isa yoko malu mandenge wangya dupwape lakyuo nyuo pipala yuu gii yanda ipingi nyepo nakamana Kamongo Anatu dokona lenge kambu dokona baapa lao ketae nembo rae maiyuo pisirami.  
\v 41 Kana yanda ipingi dokona yuu gii yanda ipingi nyero yuu gii mupwa ingyuo nambanaŋa lao retarami. Nakamana para pyasi wambu dupwame ee kana peparae dopako pyulu pyuo pyuo parami.  
\v 42 Nakama Isaraele enda akalipi dupwa anda kauwa dupwana yuu yanda ipingi nyepo palyuo kararami.  
\v 43 Dokona lao nakamana para pyasi dupwame nakama dopa pyuo palyuo kararaminyi kandapala dokopa Kamongo dokome Isaraele wambu yuu Isipi dokona kareyaminyi dupwa nyuo lanyuo epeyamopa nakama anda kauwa dupwana palena leyaŋa lao soo nyerami. Baa nakamana Kamongo Anatu.   
\p
\v 44 Dopako pyuo Moseseme Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu gii andake dupwa apa pyuo minyuo pyuo Kamongona kingi ketae palena lao pyuo kararami lao lamaiya.   
\s3 24:1—27:34 Lowa wakale wakale palamo. Misi lengepe Anatunya kingi mee kamenge kokwa soo lengepe bisinase yulu pyuope wambu yango kandope rolae pingipi Anatunya lao lalu lao lengepe wambu Anatunya lowa kamba lao randa nyingipi dupwana lao lowa pyasi palamo.  